  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Idiopathic or secondary osteoarthritis of the knee with Grade II to IV radiographic
             severity as defined by the modified Kellgren and Lawrence classification

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with inflammatory or post-infectious arthritis

          -  Those who had undergone previous arthroscopic treatment for knee osteoarthritis

          -  Those with isolate Grade III to IV medical compartment osteoarthritis with greater
             than 5 degrees of varus deformity.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
